.TH KAMADHENU 1 "February 2026" "Kamadhenu 2.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
kamadhenu \- udderly absurd fortune teller
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B kamadhenu
[\fB\-h\fR]
[\fB\-v\fR]
[\fB\-\-fast\fR]
[\fB\-\-mono\fR | \fB\-\-no-color\fR]
[\fB\-\-unicorn\fR]
[\fBsummon\fR | \fItext\fR | \fInumber\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B kamadhenu
displays random fortunes from a collection of 13,443 quotes, jokes, and wisdom, 
rendered through one of 109 ASCII art cows with rainbow gradient colors.
.PP
With no arguments, displays one random fortune. Use
.B summon
to enter interactive mode. Pass text to have a cow say it, 
or a number to display that many sequential fortunes.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B \-h
Display help message and exit.
.TP
.B \-v
Display version information and exit.
.TP
.B \-\-fast
Skip the typewriter effect (print instantly).
.TP
.B \-\-mono, \-\-no-color
Disable rainbow gradient colors.
.TP
.B \-\-unicorn
Chaotic rainbow mode with random RGB phase shifts. Creates wild, unexpected color combinations that vary each run.
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
.B kamadhenu
Display one random fortune.
.TP
.B kamadhenu summon
Launch interactive mode.
.TP
.B kamadhenu "Hello, world"
Display custom text in a speech bubble from a random cow.
.TP
.B kamadhenu 5
Show 5 random fortunes in sequence.
.TP
.B kamadhenu \-\-fast \-\-mono
Quick fortune without colors or animation.
.TP
.B kamadhenu \-\-unicorn "Chaos!"
Wild rainbow colors with random phase shifts.
.SH INTERACTIVE MODE
Launch with
.B kamadhenu summon.
In interactive mode, you can:
.IP \(bu 2
Press Enter for a random fortune
.IP \(bu 2
Type text to have a cow say it
.IP \(bu 2
Type a number to see N fortunes
.IP \(bu 2
Press Ctrl-C to exit
.SH FILES
All fortune and cow data is embedded in the binary. No external files required.
